originalText: A tiny water splash would do better than that!
A water sprinkler causes more pain than that!
Are you trying to hurt me with your tears?
I'll make you talk with the fishes for that!
I'll make you bleed for this!
AAARGH! I can't feel my arm!
Argh! That's gonna leave a big scar...
::Gasps for air.:: You almost... sank us all...
Ugh... I think that broke something...
Damn it. As if anglerfish struck me...
Arrgh, As if an eel had bitten me!
I'll make you burn in hell for this...
I don't like the... the cold...
I can't... move... I... I... Hnnnn...
I feel... the... cold... in... my... bones...
Where the hell are you!? I'll... I'll...
My brain is being crushed! Ugggh!
Can't... pull the cursed... thing out!
AAAAAARRGH! I think I can see the bone!
I can't go down... like this...
I'm taking... you down with me... ah...
I can't take much more of this... no... more...
Come on... I can do... this... I can make it...
Stop, drop, roll... STOP, DROP, ROLL!
It burns! Make it stop! Arrrgh!
Put it out! Put it out!
::Frantically tries to pat the fire out.::
I'll drink from all of your SKULLS!
I wanna see you all DIE!
Oooh! I don't feel so good...
I don't want to die... Please!
Spare my life, I beg of you!
No! I'm out of here! I am gone!
Ouch... It hurts like hell. ::Grabs chest.::
No! Get out... GET OUT OF MY... HEEEEEAAAAD!
Oh, you won't have me. You! Won't! Have! Meeeee-heheh!
Brrrr! Grrrr! There is an intruder in my... my... mind! Aaargh!
You'll get drenched in your own blood, fool!
Did you say goodbye to yo momma!? ::Laughs.::
You will not sail the waters for long!
The waves got your name on it...
You'll regret the day you embarked the docks!
Don't worry, the fishes await you...
Oh, looks like someone's about to... DROWN! ::Laughs.::
Where do you think you're going?
Come on, you're not gonna sleep now, are you?
Wake up, I'm not done with you yet!
There's nothing wrong with having a little poison in your blood.
Don't stop the bleeding, it's good for ya!
Can't you do better than that?
Don't drown while using that, fool.
Oh, yes... I'm back in action!
I ride the waves once more...
I-I wish to sail much more than this...
I'll use you as a fish bait!
Let's see if you can stay afloat.
How about an anchor to the bottom?
I'll beat you to a bloody pulp!
How about some blunt force trauma?
I'll carve you up like a mushroom cake!
Let's put a bloody smile on that face!
Say hello to my little friend!
This bullet's got your name on it!
This one will take you to the bottom...
Say hi to the fishes below!
You'll be gone in a puff of smoke! ::Laughs.::
Don't worry, it'll be quick and very painful...
Welcome to the green side of life...
I'll turn you into red swill!
HA! Unplugged and ready to sink!
This one will anchor you to the bottom!
I'll pin you to a wall!
I've got the bolt just for you!
A battle of the minds incoming!
I'll crush your puny little mind!
I'll turn your brain to mush!
Now you see me, now you don't.
I don't know why, but the word "hypothermia" just springs to my mind...
Do you like your bones chilled?
I hope you're wearing something warm.
You are gonna be so cool. ::Laughs.::
How about I burn that smile off your face!?
Let's heat things up a bit...
I hope you'll enjoy this warm reception...
No one will be able to fix ya after I'm done with you!
The raiding party is here. Stand fast.
Water doesn't make that kind of noise...
This is going right through you!
I'm gonna chop you into pieces!
Scatter you like a fish school!
Your carcass will feed the fish below!
